30#define ECDB_MAGIC ISC_MAGIC('E', 'C', 'D', 'B')
31#define VALID_ECDB(db) ((db) != NULL && \
32 (db)->common.impmagic == ECDB_MAGIC)
33
34#define ECDBNODE_MAGIC ISC_MAGIC('E', 'C', 'D', 'N')
35#define VALID_ECDBNODE(ecdbn) ISC_MAGIC_VALID(ecdbn, ECDBNODE_MAGIC)
36
37/*%
38 * The 'ephemeral' cache DB (ecdb) implementation. An ecdb just provides
39 * temporary storage for ongoing name resolution with the common DB interfaces.
40 * It actually doesn't cache anything. The implementation expects any stored
41 * data is released within a short period, and does not care about the
42 * scalability in terms of the number of nodes.
43 */
44
45typedef struct dns_ecdb {
46 /* Unlocked */
47 dns_db_t common;
48 isc_mutex_t lock;
49
50 /* Locked */
51 unsigned int references;
52 ISC_LIST(struct dns_ecdbnode) nodes;
53} dns_ecdb_t;
54
55typedef struct dns_ecdbnode {
56 /* Unlocked */
57 unsigned int magic;
58 isc_mutex_t lock;
59 dns_ecdb_t *ecdb;
60 dns_name_t name;
61 ISC_LINK(struct dns_ecdbnode) link;
62
63 /* Locked */
64 ISC_LIST(struct rdatasetheader) rdatasets;
65 unsigned int references;
66} dns_ecdbnode_t;
67
68typedef struct rdatasetheader {
69 dns_rdatatype_t type;
70 dns_ttl_t ttl;
71 dns_trust_t trust;
72 dns_rdatatype_t covers;
73 unsigned int attributes;
74
75 ISC_LINK(struct rdatasetheader) link;
76} rdatasetheader_t;
77
78/* Copied from rbtdb.c */
79#define RDATASET_ATTR_NXDOMAIN 0x0010
80#define RDATASET_ATTR_NEGATIVE 0x0100
81#define NXDOMAIN(header) \
82 (((header)->attributes & RDATASET_ATTR_NXDOMAIN) != 0)
83#define NEGATIVE(header) \
84 (((header)->attributes & RDATASET_ATTR_NEGATIVE) != 0)

137isc_result_t
138dns_ecdb_register(isc_mem_t *mctx, dns_dbimplementation_t **dbimp) {
139 REQUIRE(mctx != NULL);
140 REQUIRE(dbimp != NULL && *dbimp == NULL);
141
142 return (dns_db_register("ecdb", dns_ecdb_create, NULL, mctx, dbimp));
143}
144
145void
146dns_ecdb_unregister(dns_dbimplementation_t **dbimp) {
147 REQUIRE(dbimp != NULL && *dbimp != NULL);
148
149 dns_db_unregister(dbimp);
150}

155
156static void
157attach(dns_db_t *source, dns_db_t **targetp) {
158 dns_ecdb_t *ecdb = (dns_ecdb_t *)source;
159
160 REQUIRE(VALID_ECDB(ecdb));
161 REQUIRE(targetp != NULL && *targetp == NULL);
162
163 LOCK(&ecdb->lock);
164 ecdb->references++;
165 UNLOCK(&ecdb->lock);
166
167 *targetp = source;
168}
169
170static void
171destroy_ecdb(dns_ecdb_t **ecdbp) {
172 dns_ecdb_t *ecdb = *ecdbp;
173 isc_mem_t *mctx = ecdb->common.mctx;
174
175 if (dns_name_dynamic(&ecdb->common.origin))
176 dns_name_free(&ecdb->common.origin, mctx);
177
178 isc_mutex_destroy(&ecdb->lock);
179
180 ecdb->common.impmagic = 0;
181 ecdb->common.magic = 0;
182
183 isc_mem_putanddetach(&mctx, ecdb, sizeof(*ecdb));
184
185 *ecdbp = NULL;
186}
187
188static void
189detach(dns_db_t **dbp) {
190 dns_ecdb_t *ecdb;
191 bool need_destroy = false;
192
193 REQUIRE(dbp != NULL);
194 ecdb = (dns_ecdb_t *)*dbp;
195 REQUIRE(VALID_ECDB(ecdb));
196
197 LOCK(&ecdb->lock);
198 ecdb->references--;
199 if (ecdb->references == 0 && ISC_LIST_EMPTY(ecdb->nodes))
200 need_destroy = true;
201 UNLOCK(&ecdb->lock);
202
203 if (need_destroy)
204 destroy_ecdb(&ecdb);
205
206 *dbp = NULL;
207}
208
209static void
210attachnode(dns_db_t *db, dns_dbnode_t *source, dns_dbnode_t **targetp) {
211 dns_ecdb_t *ecdb = (dns_ecdb_t *)db;
212 dns_ecdbnode_t *node = (dns_ecdbnode_t *)source;
213
214 REQUIRE(VALID_ECDB(ecdb));
215 REQUIRE(VALID_ECDBNODE(node));
216 REQUIRE(targetp != NULL && *targetp == NULL);
217
218 LOCK(&node->lock);
219 INSIST(node->references > 0);
220 node->references++;
221 INSIST(node->references != 0); /* Catch overflow. */
222 UNLOCK(&node->lock);
223
224 *targetp = node;
225}
226
227static void
228destroynode(dns_ecdbnode_t *node) {
229 isc_mem_t *mctx;
230 dns_ecdb_t *ecdb = node->ecdb;
231 bool need_destroydb = false;
232 rdatasetheader_t *header;
233
234 mctx = ecdb->common.mctx;
235
236 LOCK(&ecdb->lock);
237 ISC_LIST_UNLINK(ecdb->nodes, node, link);
238 if (ecdb->references == 0 && ISC_LIST_EMPTY(ecdb->nodes))
239 need_destroydb = true;
240 UNLOCK(&ecdb->lock);
241
242 dns_name_free(&node->name, mctx);
243
244 while ((header = ISC_LIST_HEAD(node->rdatasets)) != NULL) {
245 unsigned int headersize;
246
247 ISC_LIST_UNLINK(node->rdatasets, header, link);
248 headersize =
249 dns_rdataslab_size((unsigned char *)header,
250 sizeof(*header));
251 isc_mem_put(mctx, header, headersize);
252 }
253
254 isc_mutex_destroy(&node->lock);
255
256 node->magic = 0;
257 isc_mem_put(mctx, node, sizeof(*node));
258
259 if (need_destroydb)
260 destroy_ecdb(&ecdb);
261}
262
263static void
264detachnode(dns_db_t *db, dns_dbnode_t **nodep) {
265 dns_ecdb_t *ecdb = (dns_ecdb_t *)db;
266 dns_ecdbnode_t *node;
267 bool need_destroy = false;
268
269 REQUIRE(VALID_ECDB(ecdb));
270 REQUIRE(nodep != NULL);
271 node = (dns_ecdbnode_t *)*nodep;
272 REQUIRE(VALID_ECDBNODE(node));
273
274 UNUSED(ecdb); /* in case REQUIRE() is empty */
275
276 LOCK(&node->lock);
277 INSIST(node->references > 0);
278 node->references--;
279 if (node->references == 0)
280 need_destroy = true;
281 UNLOCK(&node->lock);
282
283 if (need_destroy)
284 destroynode(node);
285
286 *nodep = NULL;
287}

335static isc_result_t
336findnode(dns_db_t *db, const dns_name_t *name, bool create,
337 dns_dbnode_t **nodep)
338{
339 dns_ecdb_t *ecdb = (dns_ecdb_t *)db;
340 isc_mem_t *mctx;
341 dns_ecdbnode_t *node;
342 isc_result_t result;
343
344 REQUIRE(VALID_ECDB(ecdb));
345 REQUIRE(nodep != NULL && *nodep == NULL);
346
347 UNUSED(name);
348
349 if (create != true) {
350 /* an 'ephemeral' node is never reused. */
351 return (ISC_R_NOTFOUND);
352 }
353
354 mctx = ecdb->common.mctx;
355 node = isc_mem_get(mctx, sizeof(*node));
356 if (node == NULL)
357 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
358
359 isc_mutex_init(&node->lock);
360
361 dns_name_init(&node->name, NULL);
362 result = dns_name_dup(name, mctx, &node->name);
363 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS) {
364 isc_mutex_destroy(&node->lock);
365 isc_mem_put(mctx, node, sizeof(*node));
366 return (result);
367 }
368 node->ecdb= ecdb;
369 node->references = 1;
370 ISC_LIST_INIT(node->rdatasets);
371
372 ISC_LINK_INIT(node, link);
373
374 LOCK(&ecdb->lock);
375 ISC_LIST_APPEND(ecdb->nodes, node, link);
376 UNLOCK(&ecdb->lock);
377
378 node->magic = ECDBNODE_MAGIC;
379
380 *nodep = node;
381
382 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
383}
384
385static void
386bind_rdataset(dns_ecdb_t *ecdb, dns_ecdbnode_t *node,
387 rdatasetheader_t *header, dns_rdataset_t *rdataset)
388{
389 unsigned char *raw;
390
391 /*
392 * Caller must be holding the node lock.
393 */
394
395 REQUIRE(!dns_rdataset_isassociated(rdataset));
396
397 rdataset->methods = &rdataset_methods;
398 rdataset->rdclass = ecdb->common.rdclass;
399 rdataset->type = header->type;
400 rdataset->covers = header->covers;
401 rdataset->ttl = header->ttl;
402 rdataset->trust = header->trust;
403 if (NXDOMAIN(header))
404 rdataset->attributes |= DNS_RDATASETATTR_NXDOMAIN;
405 if (NEGATIVE(header))
406 rdataset->attributes |= DNS_RDATASETATTR_NEGATIVE;
407
408 rdataset->private1 = ecdb;
409 rdataset->private2 = node;
410 raw = (unsigned char *)header + sizeof(*header);
411 rdataset->private3 = raw;
412 rdataset->count = 0;
413
414 /*
415 * Reset iterator state.
416 */
417 rdataset->privateuint4 = 0;
418 rdataset->private5 = NULL;
419
420 INSIST(node->references > 0);
421 node->references++;
422}
423
424static isc_result_t
425addrdataset(dns_db_t *db, dns_dbnode_t *node, dns_dbversion_t *version,
426 isc_stdtime_t now, dns_rdataset_t *rdataset, unsigned int options,
427 dns_rdataset_t *addedrdataset)
428{
429 dns_ecdb_t *ecdb = (dns_ecdb_t *)db;
430 isc_region_t r;
431 isc_result_t result = ISC_R_SUCCESS;
432 isc_mem_t *mctx;
433 dns_ecdbnode_t *ecdbnode = (dns_ecdbnode_t *)node;
434 rdatasetheader_t *header;
435
436 REQUIRE(VALID_ECDB(ecdb));
437 REQUIRE(VALID_ECDBNODE(ecdbnode));
438
439 UNUSED(version);
440 UNUSED(now);
441 UNUSED(options);
442
443 mctx = ecdb->common.mctx;
444
445 LOCK(&ecdbnode->lock);
446
447 /*
448 * Sanity check: this implementation does not allow overriding an
449 * existing rdataset of the same type.
450 */
451 for (header = ISC_LIST_HEAD(ecdbnode->rdatasets); header != NULL;
452 header = ISC_LIST_NEXT(header, link)) {
453 INSIST(header->type != rdataset->type ||
454 header->covers != rdataset->covers);
455 }
456
457 result = dns_rdataslab_fromrdataset(rdataset, mctx,
458 &r, sizeof(rdatasetheader_t));
459 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
460 goto unlock;
461
462 header = (rdatasetheader_t *)r.base;
463 header->type = rdataset->type;
464 header->ttl = rdataset->ttl;
465 header->trust = rdataset->trust;
466 header->covers = rdataset->covers;
467 header->attributes = 0;
468 if ((rdataset->attributes & DNS_RDATASETATTR_NXDOMAIN) != 0)
469 header->attributes |= RDATASET_ATTR_NXDOMAIN;
470 if ((rdataset->attributes & DNS_RDATASETATTR_NEGATIVE) != 0)
471 header->attributes |= RDATASET_ATTR_NEGATIVE;
472 ISC_LINK_INIT(header, link);
473 ISC_LIST_APPEND(ecdbnode->rdatasets, header, link);
474
475 if (addedrdataset == NULL)
476 goto unlock;
477
478 bind_rdataset(ecdb, ecdbnode, header, addedrdataset);
479
480 unlock:
481 UNLOCK(&ecdbnode->lock);
482
483 return (result);
484}

510static isc_result_t
511allrdatasets(dns_db_t *db, dns_dbnode_t *node, dns_dbversion_t *version,
512 isc_stdtime_t now, dns_rdatasetiter_t **iteratorp)
513{
514 dns_ecdb_t *ecdb = (dns_ecdb_t *)db;
515 dns_ecdbnode_t *ecdbnode = (dns_ecdbnode_t *)node;
516 isc_mem_t *mctx;
517 ecdb_rdatasetiter_t *iterator;
518
519 REQUIRE(VALID_ECDB(ecdb));
520 REQUIRE(VALID_ECDBNODE(ecdbnode));
521
522 mctx = ecdb->common.mctx;
523
524 iterator = isc_mem_get(mctx, sizeof(ecdb_rdatasetiter_t));
525 if (iterator == NULL)
526 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
527
528 iterator->common.magic = DNS_RDATASETITER_MAGIC;
529 iterator->common.methods = &rdatasetiter_methods;
530 iterator->common.db = db;
531 iterator->common.node = NULL;
532 attachnode(db, node, &iterator->common.node);
533 iterator->common.version = version;
534 iterator->common.now = now;
535
536 *iteratorp = (dns_rdatasetiter_t *)iterator;
537
538 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
539}

592static isc_result_t
593dns_ecdb_create(isc_mem_t *mctx, const dns_name_t *origin, dns_dbtype_t type,
594 dns_rdataclass_t rdclass, unsigned int argc, char *argv[],
595 void *driverarg, dns_db_t **dbp)
596{
597 dns_ecdb_t *ecdb;
598 isc_result_t result;
599
600 REQUIRE(mctx != NULL);
601 REQUIRE(origin == dns_rootname);
602 REQUIRE(type == dns_dbtype_cache);
603 REQUIRE(dbp != NULL && *dbp == NULL);
604
605 UNUSED(argc);
606 UNUSED(argv);
607 UNUSED(driverarg);
608
609 ecdb = isc_mem_get(mctx, sizeof(*ecdb));
610 if (ecdb == NULL)
611 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
612
613 ecdb->common.attributes = DNS_DBATTR_CACHE;
614 ecdb->common.rdclass = rdclass;
615 ecdb->common.methods = &ecdb_methods;
616 dns_name_init(&ecdb->common.origin, NULL);
617 result = dns_name_dupwithoffsets(origin, mctx, &ecdb->common.origin);
618 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS) {
619 isc_mem_put(mctx, ecdb, sizeof(*ecdb));
620 return (result);
621 }
622
623 isc_mutex_init(&ecdb->lock);
624
625 ecdb->references = 1;
626 ISC_LIST_INIT(ecdb->nodes);
627
628 ecdb->common.mctx = NULL;
629 isc_mem_attach(mctx, &ecdb->common.mctx);
630 ecdb->common.impmagic = ECDB_MAGIC;
631 ecdb->common.magic = DNS_DB_MAGIC;
632
633 *dbp = (dns_db_t *)ecdb;
634
635 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
636}

642static void
643rdataset_disassociate(dns_rdataset_t *rdataset) {
644 dns_db_t *db = rdataset->private1;
645 dns_dbnode_t *node = rdataset->private2;
646
647 dns_db_detachnode(db, &node);
648}
649
650static isc_result_t
651rdataset_first(dns_rdataset_t *rdataset) {
652 unsigned char *raw = rdataset->private3;
653 unsigned int count;
654
655 count = raw[0] * 256 + raw[1];
656 if (count == 0) {
657 rdataset->private5 = NULL;
658 return (ISC_R_NOMORE);
659 }
660#if DNS_RDATASET_FIXED
661 raw += 2 + (4 * count);
662#else
663 raw += 2;
664#endif
665 /*
666 * The privateuint4 field is the number of rdata beyond the cursor
667 * position, so we decrement the total count by one before storing
668 * it.
669 */
670 count--;
671 rdataset->privateuint4 = count;
672 rdataset->private5 = raw;
673
674 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
675}
676
677static isc_result_t
678rdataset_next(dns_rdataset_t *rdataset) {
679 unsigned int count;
680 unsigned int length;
681 unsigned char *raw;
682
683 count = rdataset->privateuint4;
684 if (count == 0)
685 return (ISC_R_NOMORE);
686 count--;
687 rdataset->privateuint4 = count;
688 raw = rdataset->private5;
689 length = raw[0] * 256 + raw[1];
690#if DNS_RDATASET_FIXED
691 raw += length + 4;
692#else
693 raw += length + 2;
694#endif
695 rdataset->private5 = raw;
696
697 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
698}
699
700static void
701rdataset_current(dns_rdataset_t *rdataset, dns_rdata_t *rdata) {
702 unsigned char *raw = rdataset->private5;
703 isc_region_t r;
704 unsigned int length;
705 unsigned int flags = 0;
706
707 REQUIRE(raw != NULL);
708
709 length = raw[0] * 256 + raw[1];
710#if DNS_RDATASET_FIXED
711 raw += 4;
712#else
713 raw += 2;
714#endif
715 if (rdataset->type == dns_rdatatype_rrsig) {
716 if ((*raw & DNS_RDATASLAB_OFFLINE) != 0)
717 flags |= DNS_RDATA_OFFLINE;
718 length--;
719 raw++;
720 }
721 r.length = length;
722 r.base = raw;
723 dns_rdata_fromregion(rdata, rdataset->rdclass, rdataset->type, &r);
724 rdata->flags |= flags;
725}
726
727static void
728rdataset_clone(dns_rdataset_t *source, dns_rdataset_t *target) {
729 dns_db_t *db = source->private1;
730 dns_dbnode_t *node = source->private2;
731 dns_dbnode_t *cloned_node = NULL;
732
733 attachnode(db, node, &cloned_node);
734 *target = *source;
735
736 /*
737 * Reset iterator state.
738 */
739 target->privateuint4 = 0;
740 target->private5 = NULL;
741}
742
743static unsigned int
744rdataset_count(dns_rdataset_t *rdataset) {
745 unsigned char *raw = rdataset->private3;
746 unsigned int count;
747
748 count = raw[0] * 256 + raw[1];
749
750 return (count);
751}
752
753static void
754rdataset_settrust(dns_rdataset_t *rdataset, dns_trust_t trust) {
755 rdatasetheader_t *header = rdataset->private3;
756
757 header--;
758 header->trust = rdataset->trust = trust;
759}

761/*
762 * Rdataset Iterator Methods
763 */
764
765static void
766rdatasetiter_destroy(dns_rdatasetiter_t **iteratorp) {
767 isc_mem_t *mctx;
768 union {
769 dns_rdatasetiter_t *rdatasetiterator;
770 ecdb_rdatasetiter_t *ecdbiterator;
771 } u;
772
773 REQUIRE(iteratorp != NULL);
774 REQUIRE(DNS_RDATASETITER_VALID(*iteratorp));
775
776 u.rdatasetiterator = *iteratorp;
777
778 mctx = u.ecdbiterator->common.db->mctx;
779 u.ecdbiterator->common.magic = 0;
780
781 dns_db_detachnode(u.ecdbiterator->common.db,
782 &u.ecdbiterator->common.node);
783 isc_mem_put(mctx, u.ecdbiterator,
784 sizeof(ecdb_rdatasetiter_t));
785
786 *iteratorp = NULL;
787}
788
789static isc_result_t
790rdatasetiter_first(dns_rdatasetiter_t *iterator) {
791 ecdb_rdatasetiter_t *ecdbiterator = (ecdb_rdatasetiter_t *)iterator;
792 dns_ecdbnode_t *ecdbnode = (dns_ecdbnode_t *)iterator->node;
793
794 REQUIRE(DNS_RDATASETITER_VALID(iterator));
795
796 if (ISC_LIST_EMPTY(ecdbnode->rdatasets))
797 return (ISC_R_NOMORE);
798 ecdbiterator->current = ISC_LIST_HEAD(ecdbnode->rdatasets);
799 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
800}
801
802static isc_result_t
803rdatasetiter_next(dns_rdatasetiter_t *iterator) {
804 ecdb_rdatasetiter_t *ecdbiterator = (ecdb_rdatasetiter_t *)iterator;
805
806 REQUIRE(DNS_RDATASETITER_VALID(iterator));
807
808 ecdbiterator->current = ISC_LIST_NEXT(ecdbiterator->current, link);
809 if (ecdbiterator->current == NULL)
810 return (ISC_R_NOMORE);
811 else
812 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
813}
814
815static void
816rdatasetiter_current(dns_rdatasetiter_t *iterator, dns_rdataset_t *rdataset) {
817 ecdb_rdatasetiter_t *ecdbiterator = (ecdb_rdatasetiter_t *)iterator;
818 dns_ecdb_t *ecdb;
819
820 ecdb = (dns_ecdb_t *)iterator->db;
821 REQUIRE(VALID_ECDB(ecdb));
822
823 bind_rdataset(ecdb, iterator->node, ecdbiterator->current, rdataset);
824}
